《[[美式懸罪|美式懸罪]]》（{{lang-en|''American Crime''}}）是一部由[[約翰·里德利|約翰·里德利]]開創，於2015年3月5日在[[美國廣播公司|ABC]]開播的[[詩選劇|詩選]][[犯罪片|犯罪電視劇]]。<ref name="TVBTN">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2014/11/19/abc-announces-premiere-dates-for-american-crime-and-secrets-and-lies/329680/|title=ABC Announces Premiere Dates for 'American Crime' and 'Secrets and Lies'|last=Kondolojy|first=Amanda|publisher=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|date=2014-11-19|accessdate=2014-11-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Alessandra |last=Stanley |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/05/arts/television/review-american-crime-a-series-where-justice-is-far-from-black-or-white.html |title=Review: ‘American Crime,’ a Series Where Justice Is Far From Black or White |work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |date=2015-03-04 |accessdate=2015-03-05}}</ref>

2015年5月7日，ABC宣布續訂第2季。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/american-crime-castle-agents-of-shield-agent-carter-galavant-secrets-lies-fresh-off-the-boat-renewed-abc-1201422717/ |title=‘American Crime’, ‘Castle’ ‘S.H.I.E.L.D.’, ‘Agent Carter’, ‘Galavant’, ‘Secrets & Lies’, ‘Nashville’ Among ABC Renewals |publisher=Deadline.com |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=2015-05-07 |accessdate=2015-05-08}}</ref>第2季搶先於2015年12月17日在網路上首播，<ref>{{cite web|last=Krolak|first=Mike|title=Watch American Crime Season 2 Premiere Online Free: Early Release|url=http://abc.go.com/shows/american-crime/news/updates/watch-american-crime-season-2-premiere-online-free-151217|publisher=ABC|accessdate=2015-12-21|date=2015-12-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Friedlander|first=Whitney|title=USA's 'Colony,' Fox's 'Second Chance' Receive Early Premieres Online|url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/usa-colony-premiere-online-second-chance-american-crime-1201666345/|accessdate=2015-12-22|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|date=2015-12-21}}</ref>並於2016年1月6日正式在ABC首播。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/american-crime-season-2-premiere-date-time-slot-abc-1201611658/|title='American Crime' Gets January Return Date, New Time Slot on ABC|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-11-06|accessdate=2015-11-06}}</ref>2016年5月12日，ABC宣布續訂第3季。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2016/05/12/american-crime-renewed-abc-season-3/ |title=American Crime Renewed at ABC |publisher=TVLine |first=Michael |last=Ausiello |date=2016-05-12 |accessdate=2016-05-12}}</ref>

